-Graphing:
-Stats about Correlations and Lags



-Strategy to employ and returns
    *entry;
        when ratio is #-##

    *exit.
        when it crosses #-##
    
    *Profit n Loss


Risks of this strategy:
    
    * Loss in correlation;
    * Specific risk to one of the firms [internal scandals]
    
    * Fees


After Strategy is built:
    *Search for Pairs;
        * Same company diferent stock class/ seniority;



